<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM3.2.2">
<l>vaṉmā vaiya maḷantavem vāmaṉāniṉ</l>
<l>paṉmā māyap palpiṟaviyiṟ paṭikiṉṟayāṉ</l>
<l>toṉmā valviṉait toṭarkaḷai mutalarintu</l>
<l>niṉmātāḷ cērntu niṟpateñ ñāṉṟukolō</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O our dwarf who measured the strong big world,</l>
<l>I who am settled in many births [due] to you many great illusionary powers,</l>
<l>cutting the root of [my] links with ancient, great, strong karma,</l>
<l>which day will I stand joined to your dark/great feet?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
